      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m absolutely thrilled to put my pride and joy up for sale. Honestly, this car is a total dream\u2014it's been kept in absolutely pristine condition and looks just as good as the day it rolled off the lot! It's been pampered, garage-kept, and is ready for a new home where it'll be just as loved. You really have to see it to believe how spotless it is. Feel free to reach out with any questions!",
